1.0.0 - May 11, 2026
=====================

  - Rewrite in Python+Qt6 (PyQt6)
  - New modern UI with QListView-based collection
  - VM creation wizard (QWizard)
  - Libvirt integration via libvirt-python
  - SPICE display support
  - Shared folders management
  - ISO media detection and download
  - Unattended OS installation support
  - Snapshot management (future)
  - All git history rewritten to new project identity
